&lt;h4&gt;Passive Information gathering&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="passive-information-gathering"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#passive-information-gathering" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Web app recon is the process of mapping an application’s endpoints, parameters, and behavior to understand its attack surface.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong recon focuses on logic and hidden functionality, not just running automated tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
